# 🧩 2. Understand VS Code architecture (important)

### Processes

```text
Main Process (Electron)
  → controls BrowserWindow, BrowserView

Renderer (Workbench UI)
  → editors, tabs, panels

Extension Host
  → your extensions (ignore for now)
```

👉 `BrowserView` must be created in **MAIN PROCESS**.

